com.soteradefense.dga.hbse

Class PartialDependency

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.soteradefense.dga.hbse.PartialDependency
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Writable

    public class PartialDependency
extends Object
implements Writable
    Represents a source vertex's dependency on a specific target vertex.

    For more information about pair dependencies and betweenness centrality see "U. Brandes, A Faster Algorithm for Betweenness Centrality"
